---
interface Props {
  galaxy: unknown;
}

const { galaxy } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
  <!-- Absolute Zero-Cost Capaldi-Style Clockwork Spiral Vortex Layer -->
  <div id="vortex-loader" class="fixed inset-0 z-[100] transition-opacity duration-1000 ease-in-out pointer-events-none" style="background: #000205;">
    
    <div class="vortex-container">
      <!-- 
        Extremely performant single flat node. 
        Optical illusion provided by repeating radial/conic gradients in CSS. 
      -->
      <div class="clockwork-tunnel"></div>
      
      <!-- Distant Golden Time Vortex Core -->
      <div class="vortex-core-glow"></div>
      
      <!-- Deep Space Vignette (Static Depth Faker) -->
      <div class="vortex-vignette"></div>

      <!-- Occasional Drift Asteroids / Planets for scale -->
      <div class="asteroid ast-1"></div>
      <div class="asteroid ast-2"></div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div id="canvas-container" class="absolute inset-0"></div>
  <div
    id="webgl-fallback"
    class="hidden absolute left-6 right-6 top-24 z-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/70 p-4 text-sm text-slate-300"
  >
    当前设备暂时无法初始化星系场景，已切换为静态模式。
  </div>
  <script
    is:inline
    id="galaxy-scene-data"
    type="application/json"
    set:html={JSON.stringify(galaxy)}
  ></script>
</section>
